flowRoot.flowPara: To see weather information, enter the name of a nearby city.
Forecast is shown from the current time slot. Eg. If it is 12:45, the first time slot is 12:00 - 13:00. It is not possible to navigate into the past.
If it is after 20:00 (?), default to tomorrow rather than today.
When showing tomorrow, default to 9:00 as the start time.
You can pan forward to the end of the day.
After 20:00, it is still possible to view today.
When there are no previous searches, a hint is displayed instead of previously used locations.
Up to five previously used locations are displayed when the popover is opened.
The search field is automatically focused.
Search results are shown in the list below the search box. Selecting a result closes the popover and switches the location in the main view.
